<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Grateful Dead Show Browser</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/jpeg" href="/images/steal-your-face.jpg">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/grateful-dead-theme.css?v=5" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    /* Remove default body margins and make full height */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    
    /* Make container take full viewport */
    .container-fluid {
      height: 100vh;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    /* Make tab content areas fill remaining space */
    .tab-content {
      background-color: transparent;
      border-radius: 0;
      padding: 0.25rem;
      margin-top: 0;
      box-shadow: none;
      position: relative;
      flex: 1;
      height: calc(100vh - 25px); /* Subtract header height */
      overflow-y: auto;
    } 
  
      /* Make tab panes fill full height */
    .tab-pane {
      height: 100%;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 0.25rem;
    }
    
    /* Add a default background for the About tab if needed */
    .tab-pane#about {
      background-image: url('/images/gd-tapes.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 0;
    }
    
    /* Ensure all content is visible over backgrounds */
    .tab-pane .card,
    .tab-pane .form-control,
    .tab-pane .form-select,
    .tab-pane .alert {
      background-color: rgba(242, 240, 230, 0.9); /* Softer off-white from --gd-background */
      color: var(--gd-text);
    }
  
    /* Style the tabs at the top */
    .nav-tabs {
      border-bottom: none;
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
    }
    
    .nav-tabs .nav-link {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
      border-radius: 0.2rem 0.2rem 0 0;
      margin-left: 0.15rem;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      color: var(--gd-text);
      border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }
    
    .nav-tabs .nav-link:hover {
      background-color: rgba(26, 147, 111, 0.1);
      border-color: #1a936f;
    }
    
    .nav-tabs .nav-link.active {
      background-color: #1a936f;
      color: white;
      border-color: #1a936f;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Header layout - more compact */
    .brand-logo {
      height: 16px;
      margin-right: 0.3rem;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    
    /* Compact header */
    .header-section {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      padding: 0.15rem 0.3rem;
      min-height: 25px;
      max-height: 25px;
    }
    
    .header-section h2 {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      margin: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-between {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .nav-tabs-container {
        max-width: 100%;
        margin-top: 0.3rem;
      }
      .nav-tabs {
        justify-content: center !important;
      }
      .header-section {
        min-height: 35px;
        max-height: 35px;
      }
      
      .tab-content {
        height: calc(100vh - 35px);
      }
    }
    
    /* Text file content */
    .text-file-content {
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      max-height: 145px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      font-family: monospace;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      color: var(--gd-text);
      padding: 3px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      font-size: 9px;
    }

    /* Audio table styling */
    .table {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      color: var(--gd-text);
      font-size: 9px;
    }
    
    .table thead th,
    .table tbody td {
      padding: 2px 3px;
    }
    
    /* Reduce margins and padding for better space utilization */
    .tab-pane h3 {
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    
    .tab-pane h4 {
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
    }
    
    .tab-pane .mb-4 {
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem !important;
    }
    
    .tab-pane .mb-3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem !important;
    }
    
    .tab-pane .row {
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }
    
    .form-label {
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
      font-size: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <!-- Navigation header with logo, title, and tabs -->
    <div class="header-section d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
      <!-- Logo and title on the left -->
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
        <img src="/images/steal-your-face.jpg" alt="Grateful Dead Logo" class="brand-logo">
        <h2 class="mb-0 me-3">Greatest Story Ever Told</h2>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Navigation tabs on the right -->
      <div class="nav-tabs-container">
        <ul class="nav nav-tabs justify-content-end" id="myTab" role="tablist"> 
          <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <button class="nav-link <%= activeTab === 'show-browser' ? 'active' : '' %>" 
                    id="show-browser-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" 
                    data-bs-target="#show-browser" type="button" role="tab" 
                    aria-controls="show-browser" aria-selected="<%= activeTab === 'show-browser' %>">
              Show Browser
            </button>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <button class="nav-link <%= activeTab === 'folder-analysis' ? 'active' : '' %>" 
                    id="folder-analysis-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" 
                    data-bs-target="#folder-analysis" type="button" role="tab" 
                    aria-controls="folder-analysis" aria-selected="<%= activeTab === 'folder-analysis' %>">
              Folder Analysis
            </button>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <button class="nav-link <%= activeTab === 'about' ? 'active' : '' %>" 
                    id="about-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" 
                    data-bs-target="#about" type="button" role="tab" 
                    aria-controls="about" aria-selected="<%= activeTab === 'about' %>">
              About
            </button>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Tab content -->
    <div class="tab-content" id="myTabContent">
      <!-- Show Browser Tab -->
      <div class="tab-pane fade <%= activeTab === 'show-browser' ? 'show active' : '' %>" 
           id="show-browser" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="show-browser-tab">
        <div class="row">
          <!-- Left Column: Pick a show + Check the setlist -->
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <!-- Pick a show section -->
            <div class="mb-4">
              <h3>Pick a show</h3>
              
              <!-- Analysis results checkbox -->
              <div class="mb-3 form-check" id="analysis-check-container" style="display: none;">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="use-analysis">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="use-analysis">Use analysis results</label>
              </div>

              <!-- Music Library Path and Library Selection -->
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                  <label for="music-library-path" class="form-label">Music Library Path:</label>
                  <select class="form-select" id="music-library-path">
                    <option value="/Users/zackrobertshaw/all_flac_music">Local Drive</option>
                    <option value="/Volumes/PiMedia/network_all_flac_music">Network Drive</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                  <label for="artist-select" class="form-label">Choose Library:</label>
                  <select class="form-select" id="artist-select" disabled>
                    <option value="">Loading libraries...</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Year carousel (for Grateful Dead) -->
              <div class="mb-3" id="year-carousel-container" style="display: none;">
                <label id="year-carousel-label" class="form-label">Pick a Year:</label>
                <div id="year-carousel" class="year-timeline">
                  <!-- Year carousel will be dynamically generated here -->
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Artist dropdown (for Other Flac) -->
              <div class="mb-3" id="artist-dropdown-container" style="display: none;">
                <label for="artist-dropdown" id="artist-dropdown-label" class="form-label">Select Artist:</label>
                <select class="form-select" id="artist-dropdown" disabled>
                  <option value="">Loading...</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Show selection - Dropdown (for Other Flac, etc.) -->
              <div class="mb-3" id="show-select-container">
                <label for="show-select" class="form-label">Select Show:</label>
                <select class="form-select" id="show-select" disabled>
                  <option value="">Select a year first</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Show selection - Timeline (for Grateful Dead) -->
              <div id="show-timeline-container" style="display: none;">
                <label class="form-label">Select Show:</label>
                <div id="show-timeline" class="show-timeline">
                  <!-- Timeline will be dynamically generated here -->
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Right Column: Play the show -->
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div id="show-content" style="display: none;">
              <h3>Play the show</h3>
              
              <!-- Play button -->
              <div class="mb-3">
                <button id="play-concert" class="hampton-ticket-button">
                  <img src="/images/hamptonTicket.jpg" alt="Hampton Ticket - Click to Play Show" class="img-fluid" />
                </button>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Check the setlist section -->
              <div id="setlist-section">
                <h4>Check the setlist</h4>
                <div class="mb-3">
                  <select class="form-select" id="text-file-select">
                    <option value="">No text files found</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div class="text-file-content" id="text-file-content">
                  Select a text file to view its content
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
            
            <div id="no-show-selected" class="text-center mt-5">
              <h3>No show selected</h3>
              <p>Please select a year and show from the dropdown menus</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Folder Analysis Tab -->
      <div class="tab-pane fade <%= activeTab === 'folder-analysis' ? 'show active' : '' %>" 
           id="folder-analysis" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="folder-analysis-tab">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Analyze Grateful Dead Show Folders</h3>
            <p class="text-muted small">Note: This analysis will run on the "Grateful Dead" folder found in the Music Library Path specified on the "Show Browser" tab.</p>
            
            <!-- Analysis form -->
            <form id="analysis-form">
              <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="output-filename" class="form-label">Output Filename:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="output-filename" value="analysis_results.csv">
              </div>
              
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Run Analysis</button>
            </form>
          </div>
          
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <!-- Analysis results -->
            <div id="analysis-results" style="display: none;">
              <h3>Analysis Results</h3>
              
              <div class="alert alert-success" id="analysis-success-message"></div>
              
              <h4>Statistics</h4>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Total shows in database</h5>
                      <p class="card-text" id="stat-total-shows">-</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Shows with matching folders</h5>
                      <p class="card-text" id="stat-shows-with-folders">-</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Shows without matching folders</h5>
                      <p class="card-text" id="stat-missing-shows">-</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Coverage</h5>
                      <p class="card-text" id="stat-coverage">-</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Folders with no date found</h5>
                      <p class="card-text" id="stat-no-date-found">-</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Folders with invalid dates</h5>
                      <p class="card-text" id="stat-invalid-dates">-</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Unmatched valid dates</h5>
                      <p class="card-text" id="stat-unmatched-dates">-</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Download button -->
              <div class="mb-3">
                <a id="download-results" class="btn btn-success" href="#" download>Download Results</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- About Tab -->
      <div class="tab-pane fade <%= activeTab === 'about' ? 'show active' : '' %>" 
           id="about" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="about-tab">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-10 offset-md-1">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Greatest Story Ever Told</h2>
            
            <div class="row mb-4 align-items-center">
              <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <img src="/images/steal-your-face.jpg" alt="Steal Your Face" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 200px;">
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-8">
                <h3>A Flexible Music Browser with foobar2000 Integration</h3>
                <p>
                  This application provides a simple and powerful way to browse your local music collection and play it instantly with foobar2000. It's designed to be flexible, with special features for Grateful Dead fans.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">How to Use</h3>
            <ol>
              <li>Select your music library location from the **"Music Library Path"** dropdown.</li>
              <li>Choose a library, such as "Grateful Dead" or "Other Flac."</li>
              <li>Depending on your choice, select a year or an artist, and then pick a show.</li>
              <li>Click the ticket image to play the entire show in foobar2000.</li>
            </ol>

            <h3 class="mt-4">Key Features</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Dynamic Library Browsing:</strong> The interface adapts to your library's structure, whether it's organized by year (for the Grateful Dead) or by artist.</li>
              <li><strong>One-Click Playback:</strong> Seamlessly play entire albums or shows in foobar2000 with perfect, gapless track ordering.</li>
              <li><strong>Grateful Dead Folder Analysis:</strong> A specialized tool that scans your Grateful Dead collection to provide detailed statistics and coverage information.</li>
              <li><strong>Built-in Grateful Dead Database:</strong> Includes data for 2,087 verified shows, ensuring accurate analysis and browsing.</li>
              <li><strong>Text File Viewer:</strong> Read setlists and other notes included with your music files.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">foobar2000 Integration</h3>
            <p>
              This application leverages **foobar2000** for its superior audio playback capabilities, including:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Gapless playback and perfect track ordering.</li>
              <li>High-quality audio support for lossless formats like FLAC.</li>
              <li>Smart process management to ensure a smooth listening experience.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">About the Data</h3>
            <p>
              The built-in Grateful Dead show database is sourced from the comprehensive **"Every Time Played" Excel spreadsheet**, a valuable resource for collectors, available at 
              <a href="https://www.gratefuldeadbook.com/product-page/every-time-played-excel-spreadsheet" target="_blank" class="text-decoration-none">gratefuldeadbook.com</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- JavaScript -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>